{
  "stem": "19518.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With a name like yours, you can-- and with the face of-- like yours, you could get away without it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he says, I'm not going to jeopardize my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, she still worked for a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was allowed to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, all my sisters worked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And slowly my father's firms were taken over by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was not allowed-- and I mean then he was not rehired by the German overseers, and he became unemployed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as such, he had to register.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And natural my mother was never employed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she had to register with her husband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so was his mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was underage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they had the four of us on the list.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Therefore, some time in November, we received-- of '40, 1940, we had received white cards written that on that and that a day, I still remember, on December 8, 1940, with what-- whatever you can carry on you, whatever you could carry with you, come voluntarily to the station for resettlement.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, we each read those cards, and we knew that's no good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They gave us a few weeks' time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we started thinking of what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Being our-- my-- all the sisters were working, they did not have them on their list, the decision was that we going to run away to a smaller town.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my parents made the arrangements with a Pole who was rewarded for his-- for-- for staking out his life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He bought tickets for the train, and we went to Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it's true, I had my parents about a year and a half longer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We still stayed as a family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Meanwhile, there began talk about a ghetto in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
